irving ramsey wiles april 8 , 1861 - 1948 american artist , bear utica , new york . 
educate sedgwick institute great barrington , learn basics painting father , lemuel maynard wiles , focus primarily landscape . 
1879 1881 study art student league new york james carroll beckwith william merritt chase , later paris carolus-duran . 
early year work illustrator american magazine , later devote great success portraiture . 
member society american artists , preface 1897 election national academy design associate . 
wiles also member american water color society . 
painting include russian tea , lady fireplace , scallop boats , peconic . 
